OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUgandan militant escapee:  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FIS forced me to fight      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A former member of the Allied          
OL,6, Democratic Forces (ADF), the rebels    
OL,7, blamed for the recent suicide bombings 
OL,8, in Uganda's capital, says the          
OL,9, Islamic-State linked group uses fear to
OL,10, keep its recruits in line.             
OL,12,F"The group is run on Sharia. If you    
OL,13,Fsteal, you lose an arm. If you rape a  
OL,14,Fchild, you die. If you tell a lie about
OL,15,Fsomeone and you're found out, you die,"
OL,16,FPeter, whose name has been changed to  
OL,17,Fprotect his identity, told the BBC.    
OL,19,FHe chuckles rather menacingly          
OL,20,Fthroughout our conversation - seemingly
OL,21,Fto deflect from the trauma he carries. 
